UFO - Universally Flying Objects
================================

Dependencies
------------

 - GMTL (>= 0.5.4, >= 0.6.0 recommended )
 - cmake (>= 2.4)


Optional libraries
------------------

 - inVRs ( >= 1.0alpha4 )

Compiling and installing
------------------------

1) Make sure you have installed all the dependencies

2) Configure user.cmake

3) Build:

# cd build

# cmake ..
OR:
# cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local

# make

4) Install:

# make install 

Note: DO NOT set DESTDIR for "make install"! This will certainly not do what you expect.
      Instead, set CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX either in user.cmake or as parameter to cmake.
